Orlen May Get Stake in U.S. Shale Deposits, Rzeczpospolita Says

-- B y   M a c i e j   M a r t e w i c z
-- 
2011-04-29T04:59:44Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-29/orlen-may-get-stake-in-u-s-shale-deposits-rzeczpospolita-says.html
PKN Orlen SA,  Poland ’s largest oil
refiner, is close to signing an agreement to get a stake in U.S.
shale gas deposits in exchange for shares in its shale
exploratory licences in Poland, Rzeczpospolita reported, without
saying where it got the information.  The Warsaw-based newspaper didn’t name Orlen’s partner in
the deal.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
